posting_body: ['CAMBRIDGE – CENTRAL SQUARE', 'Price:', '$3,442', 'Available:', 'Now.', '1 BEDROOM - 1 BATH', 'Fantastic, modern 1 bedroom near Central Square.', 'Galley kitchen with dishwasher, disposal and microwave.', 'Walk-in closet.', 'Hardwood floors and berber carpeting.', 'Central air and Laundry in unit.', 'Hot water only included, tenant to pay for electricity.', 'Amenities include: 24 hour concierge, fitness room, bike storage and landscaped courtyard.', 'One garage parking space for $325/month.', 'Cat okay for $40/month and dog okay for $85/month (breed restrictions apply).', 'Note: Photos are of a model unit.', 'Listing# 195119160', '**NOTE: Price and availability, subject to change, without notice.', '**', 'Century 21 Avon', '1675 Massachusetts Ave.', 'Cambridge, MA 02138', '617-661-8400', 'E-mail: Click "Reply" button above.']
